      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your dedication has not been in vain; instead of erasing it, this pain reveals that you have already sacrificed something far greater than your academic identity. Please consider that the help you seek cannot just be about feeling \"better\" or moving through a phase, but about finding a structure that honors your struggle without demanding you jump immediately back to work. I am honored to listen to your experience, even if we cannot offer a quick fix or tell you to keep climbing.",
